:0.2,"chara":[{"id":390201,"pos":0}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":390201,"motion":100},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":390100,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameLeft":"Shii","textLeft":"So, um, Yuu."},{"chara":[{"id":390201}],"nameLeft":"Shii","textLeft":"I didn't want you to tear off the parts I mentioned@earlier..."},{"chara":[{"id":390201}],"nameLeft":"Shii","textLeft":"He'll die if you do that."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":390100,"motion":400,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Yuu","textRight":"Y-you didn't?! Is that so?"},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":390201},{"effect":"fadeout","id":390100}],"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":104300,"motion":0,"pos":1}]},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"Kuroe","narration":"Defeating Witches, saving people...","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"That was enough for me."},{"narration":"But then a wave of bad things came barreling in@so much faster than a blockhead like me could think."},{"narration":"I got caught in the undertow,@and there was nothing I could do."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_21932.jpg","bgmFadeOut":2000,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":104300,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":104300,"lipSynch":0,"motion":100}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(What should I do?)","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":104300,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(Who am I supposed to help?)"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":104300,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(How am I supposed to help?)"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":104300,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(How can I be righteous like Tamaki-san?)"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":104300,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(I don't know anything anymore...@What do I do...? Tamaki-san...)"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":104300}],"textClear":1},{"bgm":"bgm24_story03","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":200700,"motion":400,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":390100,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameRight":"Nagisa","textRight":"You are...THE worst!"},{"chara":[{"id":200700}],"nameRight":"Nagisa","textRight":"You've gone full swing on causing problems with@regular people!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":390201,"motion":200,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Shii","textLeft":"I'm sorry."},{"chara":[{"id":390201}],"nameLeft":"Shii","textLeft":"Yuu was just trying to protect me."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":390100,"motion":200,"pos":0},{"id":200700,"motion":0}],"nameLeft":"Yuu","textLeft":"Bad guys are dangerous, y'know?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":390201,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Shii","textLeft":"And none of them..."},{"chara":[{"id":390201}],"nameLeft":"Shii","textLeft":"...considered themselves to be ordinary citizens@anyway."},{"chara":[{"id":200700,"motion":100}],"nameRight":"Nagisa","textRight":"For the love of... Talk about lame excuses."},{"chara":[{"id":200700}],"nameRight":"Nagisa","textRight":"But I get why the two of you are \"Hotsure\" now."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":104300,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"...?"},{"chara":[{"id":200700,"motion":1}],"nameRight":"Nagisa","textRight":"Right now, this is just a \"you\" problem..."},{"chara":[{"id":200700}],"nameRight":"Nagisa","textRight":"...but if we leave it unchecked, it could become@a problem for ALL Magical Girls..."},{"chara":[{"id":104300}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"...What do you mean?"},{"chara":[{"id":200700,"motion":200}],"nameRight":"Nagisa","textRight":"Think about it."},{"chara":[{"id":200700},{"id":104300,"motion":1}],"nameRight":"Nagisa","textRight":"There are already a bunch of Magical Girls..."},{"chara":[{"id":200700}],"nameRight":"Nagisa","textRight":"...who use their powers to dodge the law."},{"chara":[{"id":200700,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"Nagisa","textRight":"But if \"I want to kill villains\"..."},{"chara":[{"id":200700}],"nameRight":"Nagisa","textRight":"...catches on as a simple and seemingly justified@sentiment..."},{"chara":[{"id":200700}],"nameRight":"Nagisa","textRight":"...and other Magical Girls start to sympathize@with it and spread it around, then..."},{"chara":[{"id":104300,"motion":200}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"Nobody's going to want to do that, though."},{"chara":[{"id":104300}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"Even if they can relate to the feeling, they'd have@a better opinion than that...!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_033.exp3.json","id":200700,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Nagisa","textRight":"The number of people who wouldn't want@to murder bad guys..."},{"chara":[{"id":200700}],"nameRight":"Nagisa","textRight":"...if they had free reign to commit violence is@probably lower than you think, Kuroe."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":104300}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"id":200700,"lipSynch":0,"motion":1,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Nagisa","textCenter":"(In this universe, where the Magia Record is@a thing...)"},{"chara":[{"id":200700,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Nagisa","textCenter":"(...spats over Grief Seeds will start to decrease...)"},{"chara":[{"id":200700,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Nagisa","textCenter":"(Compared to the Law of Cycles...)"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200700,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Nagisa","textCenter":"(...the Magia Record greatly increases the lifespan@of Magical Girls...)"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200700,"lipSynch":0,"motion":300}],"nameCenter":"Nagisa","textCenter":"(There's a very real possibility...)"},{"chara":[{"id":200700,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Nagisa","textCenter":"(...that some Magical Girls who are swimming in@extra resources...)"},{"chara":[{"id":200700,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Nagisa","textCenter":"(...will set their sights on targets other than@Witches.)"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"id":200700,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":390201,"motion":200,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Shii","textLeft":"You have a point, but considering how far back@the history of Magical Girls spans..."},{"chara":[{"id":390201}],"nameLeft":"Shii","textLeft":"...surely there would have been plenty of people@already who shared our mindset?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":200700,"motion":100},{"id":390201,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"Nagisa","textRight":"There was no way to gain sympathy from people@around the world..."},{"chara":[{"id":200700}],"nameRight":"Nagisa","textRight":"...back in the Middle Ages."},{"chara":[{"id":200700,"motion":1}],"nameRight":"Nagisa","textRight":"Nowadays, when it comes to sending out a@message and having it catch on worldwide..."},{"chara":[{"id":200700}],"nameRight":"Nagisa","textRight":"...the sky's the limit."},{"chara":[{"id":200700}],"nameRight":"Nagisa","textRight":"If you two carry this out in real time..."},{"chara":[{"id":200700}],"nameRight":"Nagisa","textRight":"...and end up reaching a mutual agreement with@people's social needs..."},{"chara":[{"id":200700}],"nameRight":"Nagisa","textRight":"...then Magical Girls could become the enemy@of society..."},{"chara":[{"id":200700,"motion":400}],"nameRight":"Nagisa","textRight":"No, of mankind as a whole."},{"chara":[{"id":390201,"lipSynch":0}],"nameLeft":"Shii","textLeft":"...[wait:1.0][chara:390201:eyeClose_1][chara:390201:lipSynch_1]I see."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":390201,"motion":100},{"id":200700,"motion":0}],"nameLeft":"Shii","textLeft":"Isn't that a rather far-off future, though?"},{"chara":[{"id":390201}],"nameLeft":"Shii","textLeft":"Humans who are satisfied with their lives..."},{"chara":[{"id":390201}],"nameLeft":"Shii","textLeft":"...would want to improve the circumstances@they live in as well, right?"},{"chara":[{"id":390201,"motion":0}],"nameLeft":"Shii","textLeft":"Wouldn't that be a healthier way of looking@at it?"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200700}],"nameRight":"Nagisa","textRight":"That is..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":200700,"motion":400}],"nameRight":"Nagisa","textRight":"[flashEffect:flashWhite2][surround:2007A01]...if I don't resort to violence instead!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":390100,"motion":400,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Yuu","textLeft":"W-waaah! I hate violeeeence!"},{"chara":[{"id":200700,"motion":1}],"nameRight":"Nagisa","textRight":"Yuu... If you're gonna stay stuck in \"yesterday,\"@and won't go to \"tomorrow\"..."},{"chara":[{"id":200700}],"nameRight":"Nagisa","textRight":"I'm gonna have to stamp you out here and now."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":390100}],"nameLeft":"Yuu","textLeft":"\"Yuu\" still can't go to tomorrow, even if you say@that, though?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":390100,"motion":100}],"nameLeft":"Yuu","textLeft":"Ah, I've got it!"},{"chara":[{"id":390100}],"nameLeft":"Yuu","textLeft":"I don't want tomorrow..."},{"chara":[{"id":390100}],"nameLeft":"Yuu","textLeft":"...but you do, right, Nagisa-chan?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":390100,"motion":1}],"nameLeft":"Yuu","textLeft":"Like, that Hotsure thing you were talking about?@The future stuff?"},{"chara":[{"id":390100}],"nameLeft":"Yuu","textLeft":"If I gave that to you, would you forgive me then?"},{"chara":[{"id":200700,"motion":100}],"nameRight":"Nagisa","textRight":"I was trying to tell you that I DON'T want that@kind of future!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":390100,"motion":300}],"nameLeft":"Yuu","textLeft":"Ehh...? First you say that you want me to go@to tomorrow, and then you say you don't..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":390100}],"nameLeft":"Yuu","textLeft":"\"Tomorrow\" is a piece of junk after all!"},{"chara":[{"id":390100,"motion":200}],"nameLeft":"Yuu","textLeft":"[flashEffect:flashWhiteSlow1]Everyone's gonna suffer when it gets here!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_060.exp3.json","id":200700,"motion":300}],"nameRight":"Nagisa","textRight":"[flashEffect:flashRed1][chara:200700:effect_shake]Grrr!"},{"chara":[{"id":200700}],"nameRight":"Nagisa","textRight":"I fear that the innn-flu-ence of Yuu's m-magic is@gonna defeat my ar-argument!"},{"chara":[{"id":200700,"motion":400}],"nameRight":"Nagisa","textRight":"Kuroe, you've gotta say something too!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":104300,"motion":200,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"I-I do?! Don't drop that on me so suddenly..."},{"chara":[{"id":104300,"motion":400}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"P-please don't fight!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":390100,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Yuu","textRight":"Yeah! Exactly!"},{"chara":[{"id":104300,"motion":0}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"H-huh?"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":104300},{"effect":"fadeout","id":390100}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_060.exp3.json","id":200700,"motion":300,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Nagisa","textCenter":"[flashEffect:flashRed1][chara:200700:effect_shake]Nngh...!"},{"chara":[{"id":200700}],"nameCenter":"Nagisa","textCenter":"Th-there's that feeling again... Yuu's magic is@m-making my head go alll..."},{"chara":[{"id":200700,"motion":100}],"nameCenter":"Nagisa","textCenter":"Have at you! I'm g-goinnng for brroke!"},{"chara":[{"id":200700,"motion":200,"mouthOpen":1}],"nameCenter":"Nagisa","textBg":"shout","textCenter":"[flashEffect:flashWhite2][surround:2007A01]Full-coverage Bubble Bombs!!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeou